 A 30-YEAR-OLD man, identified simply as Efe, has reportedly committed suicide in Okuokoko community, Okpe council area of Delta state. Sources said he was found dead in his apartment on Sunday morning after apparently ingesting poison. A friend of the deceased said he attempted suicide almost a month ago because the girlfriend wanted out of their relationship. Though uncertain about the circumstances that led to him taking poison again, he said it was generally believed that it was linked to his love affair with his girlfriend.   